— restricted to the type locality and surrounding areas in CW 
<taxonomicName box="[1469,1610,1909,1938]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Geraniaceae" genus="California" kingdom="Plantae" order="Geraniales" pageId="99" pageNumber="377" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">California</taxonomicName>
